outputs.output_descr: The contribution governed by this Agreement shall be utilized excluisively for the project Preparing for Emerging Democratic Governance in Guinea. It will be used by the recipients to contribute to supporting and accompanying democratic processes in Guinea combining information, dialogue, media and advocacy. This contribution will be administered in accordance with the regulations and rules applicable to UNDP.
